data.description: NEW PRICE IMPROVEMENT! Welcome home to this beautiful SALTWATER POOL home with a view, featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a 2-car garage nestled on a quiet cul de sac in the sought after community of Stoneybrook at Venice! The stunning in-ground pool, screened-in lanai and serene lake view is sure to check that "FLORIDA LIFESTYLE" box! The spacious living area makes it ideal for entertaining. Very spacious owner suite with large bathroom and soaking tub! Enjoy your view as you wake up in the morning and look out your bedroom slider to see the beautiful, serene pool and lake! It is conveniently located near shopping, dining, and community recreational options. This home is the perfect choice for anyone looking for a peaceful retreat in the heart of Venice.  Stoneybrook is a family friendly community with a plethora of amenities to offer including but not limited to: heated pool, spa, tennis courts, basketball courts, splash pad area, trails, fitness center and more!  This home will go fast, so call and make an appointment to see this home today!
